Overview

This dashboard shows Breach Catalog overview related to the SpyCloud Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested breach catalogs from SpyCloud.

It offers information on the number of sensitive breaches, presenting the breakdown of breaches based on main category, consumer category, and type. The top 10 sites visited by infected users and breaches categorized by title are also visible. Additionally, it illustrates the breach acquisition timeline and the breach catalog. By default, it retrieves new updates every day.
